snippet.title: Dungeons & Dining Tables (Cozy-ARPG - Indie Game)
snippet.description:
Dungeons and Dining Tables is a "Cozy-ARPG" adventure where you explore dungeons to collect rare furniture for your home. Upgrade your comfy-ness and build a thriving town while uncovering a heart warming tale of community, kinship while carving out your place in a mysterious new world.

Join our public Discord: https://discord.gg/evjAHFnEGj
- Limited Time Role available for PAXaus2023 🎉🎉🎉

Follow us on: 
TikTok https://www.tiktok.com/@catalystgames
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CatalystGamess

Enquiries to admin@catalystgames.com.au
